ory unit(Plant No.5) which includes Finishing Material Godown, Main Factory Block, H- Plant, Ancillary Block etc. and two multi-storage residential buildings along with Metallic Road worth for Reliance Spinning Mills Ltd. Khanar. This company has successfully completed construction of a three-story frame structure residential building for Reliable Yarn Industry, Duhabi. We have completed factory Building, office Building, Staff Quarter, and compound wall for Arihant Poly Packs (An undertaking of Golchha Organization) at Sonapur, Sunsari and one two-storied frame structure staff quarter. Gabion factory shed and other structures for Hulas Wires Industries, Morang and Road and other small structures for same industries. This company has successfully completed 2 units of staff quarter (3 storages) for Arihan Multifibers Ltd, Sonapur, Sunsari. Recently my company has completed the construction one unit of Factory building (Around 12000 Ft²) frame structure 40′ height. There are much more like this. Details are mentioned in the table provided here. Very recently this company has completed construction of Cement Silo, cement mill, and other structures for Arghakhachi Cement, Bhairahawa. Currently, this company is engaged in the construction of Clinker Silo, Cement silo, cement mill, Packing plant, Limestone shed and other structures for United Cement at Dhading. Which is in a final stage of completion. Apart from these, we have started construction of factory building for Bishal Maida Mill, Sunsari. Right now, this company has undertaken construction of around 7500 Ft of compound wall for Hulas Autocraft in Nawalparasi district. This is also in a final stage. This company has been pre-qualified by Nepal Telecommunication Corporation for the year 2059/060 to 2063/064 to carry out Network Extension project from the eastern region. And we are executing network extension project at various places in eastern region since last 10 years. It includes construction of RCC manholes, 